## Example Usage

```hcl
resource "appleappstoreconnect_in_app_purchase_submission" "premium" {
  in_app_purchase_id = appleappstoreconnect_in_app_purchase.premium.id

  # Ensure metadata and pricing exist before submitting.
  depends_on = [
    appleappstoreconnect_in_app_purchase_localization.premium_en,
    appleappstoreconnect_in_app_purchase_price_schedule.premium,
  ]
}
```

{{ .SchemaMarkdown | trimspace }}

## Import

Submissions can be imported using their ID:

```bash
terraform import appleappstoreconnect_in_app_purchase_submission.premium XXXXXXXXXX
```

~> **Note** Submitting is irreversible: an In-App Purchase submission cannot be withdrawn through the API. Destroying this resource only removes it from Terraform state.
